			<div id="post-1741" class="post-1741 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-advising-weekly-updates category-advisor-week">

                                <div class="postmetadata">
					<span class="meta-date"><a href="https://advising.uic.edu/professional-development-advisor-week-321-325-schedule-and-rsvp-available/" title="PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: Advisor Week (3/21 &#8211; 3/25) Schedule and RSVP available!" rel="bookmark">
						<span class="month">Mar</span>
						<span class="day">12</span>
						<span class="year">2016</span>
					</a></span>


					

					<span class="meta-author"><span>by jvolpe</span></span>

				</div>
                
				<div class="post-contents">
										<h3 class="entry-title">
					<a href="https://advising.uic.edu/professional-development-advisor-week-321-325-schedule-and-rsvp-available/" title="PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: Advisor Week (3/21 &#8211; 3/25) Schedule and RSVP available!" rel="bookmark">PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: Advisor Week (3/21 &#8211; 3/25) Schedule and RSVP available!</a>
					</h3>
                    					    <div class="post-category">Posted in <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/advising-weekly-updates/">Advising Weekly Updates</a>, <a href="https://advising.uic.edu/category/advisor-week/">Advisor Week</a></div>
                    					<div class="post-content">
					<h2 style="text-align: left" align="center">Advisor Week is one of the best weeks of the year!</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: left" align="center">(March 21st &#8211; March 25th, 2016)</h2>
<p>Advisor Week is an appreciation and professional development week dedicated to advisors and happens during UIC&#8217;s Spring Break each year. UARC is pleased to partner together with colleges and units across campus to feature our own advisors presenting their knowledge and work, show advisors ways to empower themselves, bring creative and fun skill building sessions, and provide a number of opportunities to network and get to know each other better.</p>
<blockquote><p><strong>Please RSVP for all Advisor Week activities at <a href="http://go.uic.edu/advisorweekRSVP" target="_blank">http://go.uic.edu/advisorweekRSVP</a>.</strong></p></blockquote>
<p><strong>This year&#8217;s Fourth Annual Advisor Week, being held March 21st through March 25th, has fourteen different events planned over three days!</strong> The events range and we have something to keep everyone interested. We are so pleased to have a special event planned for the evening of Wednesday, March 23rd sponsored by Summer Session &#8211; we&#8217;re going to the <strong>Harris Theater for Music and Dance</strong> for <strong>Mix at 6</strong> to see CIRCA perform their special blend of circus, dance, and performance art! It brings a little bit of summer in Millenium Park to us while there&#8217;s still some frost in the air.</p>
<p>For those who favor networking and social events close to work, we&#8217;ll also be holding our closing celebration at the new Bar Louie on South Campus on Thursday night!</p>
<p>Check out the <a href="http://advising.uic.edu/advisor-week-schedule/full-schedule-of-events/" target="_blank">full schedule of events</a> including descriptions!</p>
<p><em>Monday (3/21), the morning of Wednesday (3/23), and Friday (3/25) are reserved for unit-based advisor activities and advisor gift distribution. UARC events will be held from Tuesday, March 22nd through Thursday, March 24th.</em></p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<br class="clear" />

			</div><!-- end div post -->

		
